Package: harmonizer
Title: Harmonization of Organizational Names
Version: 0.3
Date: 2020-06-03
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Stanislav",
           family = "Vlasov",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "s.vlasov@uvt.nl")
Description: Harmonizes organizational names using steps
    described in Thoma et al. (2010) and Magerman, Looy, Bart, & Song
    (2006) and more.
License: MIT License
